(9, 'ELSS vs PPF vs NPS: Which Tax-Saving Option Should You Choose?', 'elss-vs-ppf-vs-nps-which-tax-saving-option-should-you-choose', 'Compare ELSS, PPF, and NPS on returns, lock-in, tax, and risk—plus a simple decision tree for salaried and self?employed investors.', 'ELSS: Market?linked, 3?year lock?in, potential higher returns; taxed as capital gains. Great for long?term wealth + 80C saving.\nPPF: 15?year lock?in, sovereign?backed, EEE tax status. Best for safety?first and goal?based saving.\nNPS: Low?cost market exposure with pension focus. Partial lump sum tax?free; \nrest annuitised. Ideal for retirement planning with additional 80CCD(1B) benefits.\nDecision guide: If you need safety—PPF. Want growth + 80C—ELSS. Retirement?focused with extra tax room—NPS.\nWith Ensurekar: We create a blended allocation tailored to risk profile and cash?flow needs.', 'Krishna', 'Krishna.vish9329@gmail.com', 'i am Krishna ', 'draft', 0, '1761651403484_zv66rwdieu.png', '/images/upload/blogImage/1761651403484_zv66rwdieu.png', '[\"tax saving\",\"PPF\"]', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2025-10-28 06:06:41', '2025-12-27 09:02:36', 0, 'ELSS vs PPF vs NPS: Best Tax-Saver For You | Ensurekar', 'ELSS vs PPF vs NPS: Best Tax-Saver For You | Ensurekar'),
(19, 'How to Register a Private Limited Company Online in India (2025 Guide)', 'how-to-register-private-limited-company-online-india', 'Learn how to register a private limited company online in India in 2025. This complete guide explains cost, documents, timelines, platforms, and step-by-step online company registration using digital services.', '<h3 data-start=\"990\" data-end=\"1066\">Introduction: Why Online Company Registration in India Is the New Normal</h3>\n<p data-start=\"1068\" data-end=\"1339\">If youâ€™re wondering <strong data-start=\"1088\" data-end=\"1149\">how to register a private limited company online in India</strong>, youâ€™re not alone.<br data-start=\"1168\" data-end=\"1171\">\nThousands of founders, freelancers, and startups search daily for <strong data-start=\"1237\" data-end=\"1286\">online company registration services in India</strong> â€” and today, the entire process is <strong data-start=\"1322\" data-end=\"1338\">100% digital</strong>.<br><br></p>\n<p data-start=\"1341\" data-end=\"1502\">With MCA portals, digital signatures, and professional online platforms, <strong data-start=\"1414\" data-end=\"1472\">company registration in India can now be done remotely</strong>, without visiting any office.<br><br></p>\n<p data-start=\"1504\" data-end=\"1619\">This guide answers <strong data-start=\"1523\" data-end=\"1581\">all common questions people ask online and in AI tools</strong> about company incorporation in India.<br><br></p>\n<h2 data-start=\"1626\" data-end=\"1694\">How Can I Register a Private Limited Company Online in India?<br><br>1. To <strong data-start=\"1699\" data-end=\"1753\">register a private limited company online in India</strong>, you must complete these steps digitally:</h2>\n<ol data-start=\"1797\" data-end=\"2076\">\n<li data-start=\"1797\" data-end=\"1846\">\n<p data-start=\"1800\" data-end=\"1846\">Obtain <strong data-start=\"1807\" data-end=\"1846\">Digital Signature Certificate (DSC)</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li dat