(29, 'Limited Liability Partnership Registration in India: Online Process, Cost, Documents & Best Service Providers', 'limited-liability-partnership-registration-india', 'Planning to start an LLP in India? This complete guide explains how to register a Limited Liability Partnership online, documents required, costs, benefits, and how EnsureKar helps you register your LLP quickly and compliantly.', '<h3 data-start=\"1020\" data-end=\"1088\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Introduction: Why LLP Is a Popular Business Structure in India<br><br></h3><p data-start=\"1090\" data-end=\"1444\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">A <strong data-start=\"1092\" data-end=\"1131\">Limited Liability Partnership (LLP)</strong> is one of the most preferred business structures for startups, professionals, and small businesses in India. It combines the <strong data-start=\"1257\" data-end=\"1289\">flexibility of a partnership</strong> with the <strong data-start=\"1299\" data-end=\"1344\">limited liability protection of a company</strong>, making it ideal for entrepreneurs who want compliance credibility without heavy regulatory burden.<br><br></p><p data-start=\"1446\" data-end=\"1629\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">With the Government of India enabling <strong data-start=\"1484\" data-end=\"1517\">fully online LLP registration</strong>, entrepreneurs can now register their LLP from anywhere using professional online platforms like <strong data-start=\"1615\" data-end=\"1628\">EnsureKar</strong>.<br><br></p><h2 data-start=\"1636\" data-end=\"1708\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">How Can I Register a Limited Liability Partnership Online in India?<br><br></h2><p data-start=\"1710\" data-end=\"1849\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">You can register an LLP online through the <strong data-start=\"1753\" data-end=\"1792\">Ministry of Corporate Affairs (MCA)</strong> portal with the help of a professional service provider.<br><br></p><p data-start=\"1851\" data-end=\"1896\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The online <a href=\"https://ensurekar.com/limited-liability-partnership-registration\">LLP registration proces</a>s includes:<br><br></p><ul data-start=\"1897\" data-end=\"2000\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><li data-start=\"1897\" data-end=\"1934\"><p data-start=\"1899\" data-end=\"1934\">Digital Signature Certificate (DSC)</p></li><li data-start=\"1935\" data-end=\"1953\"><p data-start=\"1937\" data-end=\"1953\">2.Name reservation</p></li><li data-start=\"1954\" data-end=\"1976\"><p data-start=\"1956\" data-end=\"1976\">3.Incorporation filing</p></li><li data-start=\"1977\" data-end=\"2000\"><p data-start=\"1979\" data-end=\"2000\">4.PAN &amp; TAN application<br><br><a data-start=\"2024\" data-end=\"2104\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_new\" class=\"decorated-link cursor-pointer\"></a></p></li></ul><p data-start=\"2002\" data-end=\"2104\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><a data-start=\"2024\" data-end=\"2104\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_new\" class=\"decorated-link cursor-pointer\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br>EnsureKar handles the entire process digitally, ensuring accuracy, faster approvals, and post-registration compliance support.</span></a></p><p data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2232\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></p><h2 data-start=\"2239\" data-end=\"2317\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Is There an Online Portal for Limited Liability Partnership Registration?<br><br></h2><p data-start=\"2319\" data-end=\"2403\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Yes. LLPs are registered through the <strong data-start=\"2356\" data-end=\"2395\"><a href=\"http://mca.gov.in/\">MCA (Ministry of Corporate Affairs)</a></strong> portal:</p><ul data-start=\"2404\" data-end=\"2430\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><li data-start=\"2404\" data-end=\"2430\"><p data-start=\"2406\" data-end=\"2430\"><br><br></p></li></ul><p data-start=\"2432\" data-end=\"2675\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">However, the MCA portal involves technical forms, legal documentation, and compliance rules. That’s why most entrepreneurs prefer <strong data-start=\"2562\" data-end=\"2599\">online LLP registration platforms</strong> like EnsureKar, which simplify the process and assign expert professionals.<br></p><h2 data-start=\"2682\" data-end=\"2769\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br>Step-by-Step Guide for Limited Liability Partnership Registration Process in India.<br><br></h2><h3 data-start=\"2771\" data-end=\"2827\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Step 1: Obtain Digital Signature Certificate (DSC)</h3><p data-start=\"2828\" data-end=\"2899\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">All designated partners must have a valid DSC to sign electronic forms.<br><br></p><h3 data-start=\"2901\" data-end=\"2961\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Step 2: Apply for Director Identification Number (DIN)</h3><p data-start=\"2962\" data-end=\"3047\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">DIN is mandatory for all designated partners and is applied along with incorporation.<br><br></p><h3 data-start=\"3049\" data-end=\"3089\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Step 3: Name Reservation (RUN-LLP)</h3><p data-start=\"3090\" data-end=\"3159\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The LLP name must be unique and compliant with MCA naming guidelines.<br><br></p><h3 data-start=\"3161\" data-end=\"3211\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Step 4: File LLP Incorporation Form (FiLLiP)</h3><p data-start=\"3212\" data-end=\"3292\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">This includes partner details, registered office address, and business activity.<br><br></p><h3 data-start=\"3294\" data-end=\"3328\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Step 5: LLP Agreement Filing</h3><p data-start=\"3329\" data-end=\"3431\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The LLP Agreement defining partner roles, profit sharing, and management must be filed within 30 days.<br><br></p><h3 data-start=\"3433\" data-end=\"3465\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Step 6: PAN &amp; TAN Issuance</h3><p data-start=\"3466\" data-end=\"3518\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 